                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Admission Ticket is valid for the selected date only. Please note the schedule may change due to various reasons. Kindly refer to the official schedule prior to your visit.Eligibility Children aged 2 year and below are free of charge. Guests aged 13 years and above are considered Adults. Guests aged 3 to 12 years old are entitled to purchase the Child rate.Attraction Access Outside food and beverages are not allowed inside the venue. Smoking and drinking are strictly prohibited. Guests caught violating this rule will be asked to leave immediately.Additional Information The main traveller’s name must match the IC / passport. Incorrect names may result in invalid redemption. Storage facilities are available at the venue. Please approach on-site staff for applicable rates. This activity is not recommended for guests with medical conditions (e.g. high blood pressure, epilepsy), pregnant women, or seniors.Important Notes Wear comfortable walking shoes, especially if planning to explore the SkyBridge. Bring sunscreen, a hat, and sunglasses for sun protection."
